<br>
2)  Port in alone and just wait with your pointer over gate, which you have memmed.  Keep waiting.  If you see &quot;Wuoshi casts a spell&quot;  Don't wait any longer, hit gate.<br>
<br>
3)  if you waited a minute and he didn't attack you then invis and slowly scout the area.  If anything casts on you while invis, its likely Wuoshi.  Hit that gate button.<br>
<br>
